Package: agrivoltaics
Title: Statistical Analysis Tool for Agrivoltaics Field Experiments
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("JK", "Kim", , "kimjk@agronomy4future.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a Shiny-based graphical interface for fitting Linear 
    Mixed Models (LMM) to agrivoltaics field experiment data. Supports 8 
    experimental layout cases covering combinations of single/multiple 
    cultivars, rows, and seasons. Based on the statistical framework 
    developed at agronomy4future.com.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
